high_descs: Turn right and walk to the small black table on the left.
Pick up the red credit card from the shelf below the table.
Turn right to face the large black desk.
Put the credit card on the left side of the desk in front of the set of keys.
Turn left to face the small black table.
Pick up the right red credit card from the table.
Turn right to face the large black desk.
Put the credit card on the far left side of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on a desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, the turn left and walk up to the small black end table.
Pick up the red credit card off of the shelf of the small black end table.
Turn right to face the desk.
Put the red credit card in front of the set of keys on the desk.
Turn left to face the small black end table.
Pick up rightmost credit card off of the small black end table.
Turn right to face the black desk.
Put the red credit card on the left side of the black desk.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to a black desk.

high_descs: Move over right to the brown end table on the right of the book shelf.
Pick up the red credit card on the bottom shelf.
Move forward and turn right towards the desk.
Place the credit card in the front of the keys.
Turn left and move back from the end table.
Pick up the red credit card no the right side nearer to the CD.
Move forward and turn right towards the desk.
Place the credit card on the left of the first credit card.
